snippet.title: Guns of Icarus Alliance Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Guns of Icarus Alliance released on March 31st!

Learn more at:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/608800/

The most teamwork airship game evolves with the release of Alliance. Face hordes of enemies, giant bosses, and constantly changing dangers.

Choose your faction, fighting for what you believe, and leaving your mark on the world with a permanent player made history.
